                <h1>Why Is Background Music on TV Too Loud?</h1>
                <p>Background music in TV shows can sometimes overpower dialogue, making it hard to follow the plot. This issue often frustrates viewers, leading them to adjust volume settings or miss important story elements. Finding the right balance between background music and dialogue is essential for an enjoyable viewing experience.</p>
